        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "Here are some pizza restaurants near you:\n\n*   **Joe's Pizza** at 124 Fulton St is a long-time family-owned pizzeria that serves classic pies and slices. They offer takeout, delivery, and dine-in options and are open from 10:00 AM to 3:00 AM.\n*   **Stage Door Pizzeria** at 26 Vesey St is a pizza parlor that offers upside-down slices and calzones. They are open from 10:00 AM to 8:00 PM and offer takeout, delivery, and dine-in options.\n*   **Famous Calabria Pizza** at 27 St James Pl offers slices, salads, and Italian entrees. They are open from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM and offer takeout, delivery, and dine-in options.\n*   **Kesté Pizza e Vino** at 77 Fulton St serves Neapolitan wood-fired pizzas with vegan and gluten-free options. They are open from 11:00 AM to 9:30 PM.\n*   **Little Italy Pizzeria and Deli** at 50 Fulton St is open 24/7 and serves a variety of thin-crust pies and slices. They offer takeout, delivery, and dine-in options.\n*   **Little Italy Pizza** at 154 Church St is a bustling late-night pizza outlet that serves hefty slices and pies. They offer takeout, delivery, and dine-in options and are open until 12:00 AM.\n*   **Little Italy Pizza - Park Place** at 11 Park Pl prepares pizza by the slice, full pies, and calzones for takeout and delivery. They are open from 10:00 AM to 7:00 PM.\n*   **Rosella's Pizzeria** at 164 William St is a casual pizza parlor that offers a variety of slices and pies, plus pastas, subs, and salads. They are open from 10:00 AM to 10:00 PM.\n*   **Abitino’s Pizza Financial District** at 32 Broadway is open from 10:00 AM to 8:00 PM and offers takeout, delivery, and dine-in options.\n*   **Traditas Pizza** at 83 Maiden Ln offers familiar slices and pies with a variety of toppings, plus pasta. They are open from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM.\n*   **Luna Pizza** at 225 Park Row is a simple eatery that serves a range of classic Italian dishes including NYC-style pizza and sandwiches. They are open from 10:00 AM to 8:40 PM.\n*   **Zia Maria Little Italy** at 138 Mulberry St serves house-made pasta, pizza, and other Italian classics. They are open from 11:00 AM to 10:00 PM.\n*   **Eataly** at 101 Liberty St is an Italian market that offers counters, restaurants, and cooking demos. They are open from 7:00 AM to 11:00 PM.\n*   **The Pie Guy Pizza** at 83-85 Baxter St serves New York-style pies along with slices and other comfort fare. They are open from 10:00 AM to 8:00 PM.\n*   **Hank's Pizza** at 110 Trinity Pl offers New York-style pies and slices plus sandwiches and salads. They are open from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM.\n*   **Siena Pizza** at 14 Rector St specializes in pizzas with a variety of toppings, plus homemade meatballs and cannoli. They are open from 11:00 AM to 11:00 PM.\n*   **Underground Pizza** at 3 Hanover Square offers NYC-style & thin-crust specialty pies plus pasta & Italian sandwiches. They are open from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM.\n*   **Lucia Pizza Of SoHo** at 375 Canal St serves a variety of thin-crust pizzas by the slice, as well as pies. They are open from 11:00 AM to 10:00 PM.\n*   **La Pizza & La Pasta** at 101 Liberty St is a casual restaurant for Italian comfort food. They are open from 11:00 AM to 10:00 PM.\n*   **Serafina Tribeca** at 95 W Broadway offers thin-crust pizza and homemade pasta. They are open from 12:00 PM to 10:00 PM.\n\nI hope this helps you find some great pizza!\n"
          }
